{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"32":{"eng-name":"Chapters on Dress","ara-name":"كتاب اللباس"}},"section_detail":{"32":{"hadithnumber_first":3550,"hadithnumber_last":3656,"arabicnumber_first":3550,"arabicnumber_last":3656}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3628,"arabicnumber":3628,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن المثنى، حدثنا ابو داود، حدثنا زهير، عن ابي اسحاق، عن ابي جحيفة، قال رايت رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم هذه منه بيضاء . يعني عنفقته","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Agreed Upon"}],"reference":{"book":32,"hadith":79},"chapter":{"id":35,"ara-name":"باب مَنْ تَرَكَ الْخِضَابَ","eng-name":"One who does not dye his hair","isFirstHadith":true}}]}